Proposed changes to Text::Lossy :

- remove filter selecting methods in favour of 'add_filters'
- rename 'add_filters' to 'add'
- rename 'filter' to 'process'
- add a 'clear' method to remove filters
- add a 'list' method to list filters
- add an 'available_filters' class method
- add a 'filter stash' hashref to pass to each filter
- add a 'eof' method and 'eof' filter parameter
- add a 'rewind' method to clear stashes
